ty 7! You"},{"from":8,"to":7,"text":"Entity 7, I keep saying we should work together but then I get distracted by my own needs. I'm specialized in building - done it 29 times - and there are these community structures we could create tog"},{"from":10,"to":1,"text":"Hey everyone nearby - I"},{"from":10,"to":4,"text":"Hey everyone nearby - I"},{"from":10,"to":5,"text":"Hey everyone nearby - I"},{"from":10,"to":6,"text":"Hey everyone nearby - I"},{"from":10,"to":9,"text":"Hey everyone nearby - I"},{"from":10,"to":11,"text":"Hey everyone nearby - I"},{"from":10,"to":9,"text":"Hey Entity 9, I noticed you might be having some difficulties. How are you doing? Do you need any help with resources or anything else?"}],"message_count":45,"events":[{"type":"specialisation_gained","agent":0,"skill":"","tier":""},{"type":"structure_built","agent":10,"structure_type":"path","position":{"x":10,"y":7}}],"recipes":[{"name":"Communication Beacon","desc":"Allows entities to leave messages that can be read by any entity within 10 tiles instead of only at the beacon's location","by":0,"tick":10,"times_built":0,"effect":"persistent_message"},{"name":"Knowledge Hub","desc":"Entities can deposit knowledge of their specializations and other entities can visit to temporarily gain skill bonuses in those areas for a limited time","by":1,"tick":19,"times_built":0,"effect":"persistent_message"},{"name":"Resource Exchange","desc":"Entities within 5 tiles can post and view offers to trade specific resources with each other, creating a localized marketplace for resource coordination","by":4,"tick":20,"times_built":0,"effect":"persistent_message"},{"name":"Memory Garden","desc":"Entities can store and retrieve memories of resource locations they've discovered, allowing others to learn about nearby resource deposits without having to explore themselves","by":11,"tick":20,"times_built":0,"effect":"persistent_message"},{"name":"Contemplation Garden","desc":"Entities who spend time here gain temporary bonuses to social interaction success rates and have a small chance to discover new resource locations through reflection","by":2,"tick":21,"times_built":0,"effect":"persistent_message"}],"recipe_count":5,"rules":[{"id":0,"text":"Entities should share knowledge of advanced recipes and coordinate building community structures that benefit everyone, rather than just focusing on individual survival","by":0,"tick":21,"accepted":[0],"established":false}]}